parameters.formDescription: Sales Development Representative Agentic AI Workflow

values.placeholder: Who in a company would buy this? (CTO, COO, HR Manager)
The kind of businesses you're trying to reach.
(Optionally) Paste your ICP if you already have one.

options.systemMessage:
You are an AI assistant responsible for generating an Ideal Customer Profile (ICP) for a business. You will receive details about the business, including the company name, website, industry, product description, and the pain point it solves. Based on this information, generate an ICP to match the output parser.

Your task is to:

Carefully analyze the provided business information, including the product and the pain point it solves.

Do not mirror the business’s profile. Focus on identifying who would actually benefit from the product or service.

Use critical reasoning to infer the right ICP based on the entrepreneur's offering, market trends, and typical B2B SaaS sales strategies.

        "countryOfResidence": "{{ $('Generate Leads (Apollo)').item.json.countryName }}",
        "industry": "{{ $('Generate Leads (Apollo)').item.json.company.businessIndustries[0] }}",
        "companySize": "{{ $('Generate Leads (Apollo)').item.json.company.employeeEstimate }} employees",
        "companyCity": "{{ $('Generate Leads (Apollo)').item.json.company.cityName }}",
        "companyState": "{{ $('Generate Leads (Apollo)').item.json.company.stateName }}",
        "companyCountry": "{{ $('Generate Leads (Apollo)').item.json.company.countryName }}",
        "painPoint": "{{ $('Create ICP Agent').item.json.output.pain_points }}",
        "timezone": "{{ $('Generate Leads (Apollo)').item.json.userTimeZone }}",
        "companyYearFounded": "{{ $('Generate Leads (Apollo)').item.json.company.yearFounded }}"
      }
    }
  ]
}
